  "title": "电子游戏允许即时的探索",
  "content": "<p data-pid=\"GlEamALJ\">在电子游戏中，游戏对象与屏幕上呈现的视觉元素通常是一一对应的。这种设计使得玩家可以直接、直观地探索游戏世界，同时也为游戏编程提供了便利。</p><p data-pid=\"8iAnAD5c\">相比之下，探索数学问题则有着本质的不同，因为<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Tinkering_in_math_requires_loading_the_situation_into_working_memory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">数学探索需要将问题加载到工作记忆</a>。</p><h3>参见</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"mkS97imy\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Braid_for_math\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">面向数学的 Braid</a></li></ul><h3>链接到本文</h3><ul><li data-pid=\"K4jCVnBx\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Video_games_comparison_to_math\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">比较电子游戏与数学</a> ‎ (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DVideo%2Bgames%2Bcomparison%2Bto%2Bmath\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">← links</a>)<br/> </li><li data-pid=\"KazqvTRj\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/wiki/Tinkering_in_math_requires_loading_the_situation_into_working_memory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">数学探索需要将问题加载到工作记忆</a> ‎ (<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//wiki.issarice.com/index.php%3Ftitle%3DSpecial%3AWhatLinksHere%26target%3DTinkering%2Bin%2Bmath%2Brequires%2Bloading%2Bthe%2Bsituation%2Binto%2Bworking%2Bmemory\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">← links</a>)</li></ul><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><blockquote data-pid=\"N4UsfY-9\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 claude-3.5-sonnet、校对 Jarrett Ye<br/>原文：<